# append(contentsOf:)

**Instance Method**

Appends the bytes in the specified array to the end of the data.

## Declaration

```swift
mutating func append(contentsOf bytes: [UInt8])
```

## Adding Bytes

- **append(_:)**: Appends the specified data to the end of this data.
- **append(_:)**: Append a buffer of bytes to the data.
- **append(_:count:)**: Appends the specified bytes from memory to the end of the data.
